A message to my non-Arab friends, 

I hope you know that everything we‚Äôre posting is for you. I am not posting for my Arab friends. This is not news to us. We grew up with this conversation in our homes. We grew up with the pain of our Palestinian friends who could not seem to get in or out of their own country. We grew up with the constant dehumanization of Arabs and vilification of Muslims. This is not news to us. 

When Palestinians are taking time to make videos in English while the world around them falls apart, I hope you realize that it‚Äôs for YOU. When we constantly share videos of the genocide, it‚Äôs so that YOU can start seeing Palestinians as more than just numbers on a news report. When we share videos of our protests, we‚Äôre trying to get the reality across to YOU. 

This genocide is funded by your governments with your own tax payer dollars. It is perpetuated by the propaganda that you are consuming. Your countries are what control the media that is silencing the Palestinian people. The plethora of information being posted is for you, it‚Äôs us trying to share with you the reality we‚Äôve known for years. 

This is not a conflict and this is not a war. This is a genocide. Don‚Äôt be complicit. Don‚Äôt blindly stand on the wrong side of history. 

